title: Walmart: The Pioneer Woman 12-Piece Dinnerware Set Only $29.98 (Regularly $49.97)
text:

Consider adding this Flea Market Decorated Floral 6.4″ Butter Dish priced at $5.46 OR one of the Pioneer Woman Clearance Items posted here to meet the free shipping threshold!
